add('Unlikelypositiveoutlook', 'http://unlikelypositiveoutlook.thecomicseries.com/', u'A tale of a young man who has girl problems. Will Mill is a 23 year old male dealing with his own personal struggle towards "growing up". On the route to adulthood with him are his best friends; couple Mitch Erikson and Lily McMeyer. A notable object of Will\'s desire is Jameson Blake. A kind and lovely gal who shows Will out of his seven year stint with Alessa Dinkley, his ex. Locations from Hollywood to Sonoma County and beyond, Unlikely Positive Outlook might just be an interesting read. Updates Sundays.') # 175
